  "body": "This issue is meant to track planned work items for pre-allocated hugepages across releases.\r\n\r\nThis issue captures the plan of record discussed in the wg-resource-mgmt meetings.\r\n\r\n## v1.9\r\n- [x] HugePages should be restricted via ResourceQuota [**Owner**: @lichuqiang , fixed #54292]\r\n\r\nAssess ability to graduate feature to beta.\r\n\r\n## 1.10\r\n- [x] HugePages should require the user to request cpu or memory [**Owner**: @tanshanshan fixed #54379]\r\n- [x] HugePages should not be tied to QoS [**Owner**: @tanshanshan fixed #54379]\r\n- [ ] HugePages promoted to beta [**Owner:** @derekwaynecarr, #56939]\r\n\r\n## Future\r\n- [ ] HugePages isolated at container and not just pod boundary [**Owner**: TBD]\r\n- [ ] HugePages should be restricted via LimitRange [**Owner**: TBD]\r\n\r\ncc @sjenning @jeremyeder @vishh @ConnorDoyle @kubernetes/sig-node-feature-requests \r\n  \r\n  ",
